OL,6,FA man from Plymouth who strangled a
OL,7,Fformer partner after their
OL,8,Frelationship ended been jailed.
OL,10,FLee Blatchford, 50, appeared at
OL,11,FPlymouth Crown Court on 24 September
OL,12,Fand pleaded guilty to controlling and
OL,13,Fcoercive behaviour, perverting the
OL,14,Fcourse of justice, assault by beating
OL,15,Fand two intentional strangulation
OL,16,Fcharges.
OL,18,FHe was sentenced to 2 years and 11
OL,19,Fmonths in jail and a restraining order
OL,20,Fwas put in place to protect the victim.
