OL,6,FShe and her daughter were eventually
OL,7,Fable to get Blatchford out of the
OL,8,Fproperty and close the door.
OL,10,FIn breach of his bail on 31 March 2024
OL,11,F, Blatchford also waited outside the
OL,12,Fvictim's property until she got home.
OL,13,FHe invited her to his property, to
OL,14,Fwhich she agreed, and provided her
OL,15,Fwith crack cocaine to convince her to
OL,16,Fstay.
OL,18,FThe victim repeatedly asked to go home
OL,19,Fand when she started collecting her
OL,20,Fbelongings, Blatchford became abusive,
OL,21,Flay on top of her and strangled her.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
