OL,6,FHe then strangled her a second time,
OL,7,Fdragging her back into the property
OL,8,Fwhenever she tried to leave. He
OL,9,Feventually allowed her to leave the
OL,10,Ffollowing morning.
OL,12,FBlatchford also made several calls
OL,13,Ffrom prison in which he asked others
OL,14,Fto contact the victim in an effort to
OL,15,Fmake her drop the case.
