OL,6,FFollowing the hearing, Domestic
OL,7,Fviolence inspector for Plymouth
OL,8,FChristopher Kinski said: "This
OL,9,Fsentence shows the commitment we have
OL,10,Fin bringing domestic violence
OL,11,Foffenders to justice.
OL,13,F"As a force domestic abuse and
OL,14,Fviolence against women is a priority,
OL,15,Fand our domestic abuse investigation
OL,16,Fteams will work tirelessly to ensure
OL,17,Fall cases are investigated fully.
