OL,6,F"We would like to thank the victim in
OL,7,Fthis case for the bravery she has
OL,8,Fshown in disclosing the abuse she has
OL,9,Fsuffered and hopefully this sentence
OL,10,Fwill allow her to be able move forward
OL,11,Fin her life.
OL,13,F"This investigation was supported by
OL,14,Four partners who assist the police in
OL,15,Fsupporting victims of domestic abuse
OL,16,Fthroughout the investigation process,
OL,17,Fcourt and after.
