OL,6,F"Our collaborative work with the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service and Plymouth City
OL,8,FCouncil will continue as we continue
OL,9,Fto strive for a safer city.
OL,11,F"I hope this sends out a clear message
OL,12,Fto the public that domestic violence
OL,13,Fwill not be tolerated in our city. If
OL,14,Fan offence of domestic abuse is
OL,15,Freported to the police, we will
OL,16,Finvestigate these offences fully and
OL,17,Fensure those perpetrators are held
OL,18,Faccountable for their actions.
